page.title: 05Biography
page.content: My name is Jesse Dargue,I am a game- keepers son.I get up about 7a.m.I get dressed and have breakfast,(Bran Flak- es and Muesli with milk).I make my packed lunch and pack my bag for school. I walk through the woods,to the road and catch the school bus at 8.45 a.m.It makes eight stops to pick up children in a village or at a track to a farm.It reaches school at 9.10 a.m. The school day lasts until 3.40p.m. when I catch the bus,(same route)home. I have tea,(sandwitch and milk)I feed my ferrets,(bread and milk or rabbits).I do my homework,practise my guitar and have supper at 6p.m.(main cooked meal). I help my dad feed his pheasants, (half an hour).Go to Youth Club or watch television until bed at 9p.m.
